This paper deals with the problem of ensuring the integrity of machine learning inference services, which involves both security and machine learning aspects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
